 filed with the securities and exchange commission in  the company raised an additional  million in capital through a secondary offering  when did the company acquire the casual male stores and when did the company change its name from casual male retail group inc formerly designs inc to destination xl group inc  in may  the company acquired at a bankruptcy court ordered auction certain assets of casual male corp the acquisition included but was not limited to approximately  casual male big  tall retail and outlet stores its catalog and ecommerce operations and various intellectual property in view of the significance of the casual male acquisition to the growth and future identify of the company on august   the board of directors recommended and the shareholders approved to change the companys name from designs inc to casual male retail group inc in fiscal  the company tested is new store concept destination xl dxl  based on the overwhelming response of the stores the company is in the process of closing all of its existing casual male xl retail stores and replacing them with dxl stores  by fiscal  the company expects to have opened up to  dxl stores  given this new direction and the importance of its dxl stores to the overall business in february  the company changed its corporate name to destination xl group inc what is your ticker symbol dxlg where are your shares traded destination xl group inc formerly casual male retail group inc and prior to that designs inc common stock is traded on the nasdaq global market can i buy stock directly from destination xl group inc destination xl group inc common stock can be bought or sold through a stockbroker or any financial institution that provides brokerage services who is your transfer agent american stock transfer  trust company  maiden lane plaza level new york ny  toll free  x wwwamstockcom infoamstockcom how can i obtain financial information such as your annual report you can request this information in a number of ways online request go to our investor relations home page and click on information request email investorrelationsdxlgcom mail  destination xl group inc           investor relations            turnpike street           canton ma            phone   how can i obtain sec documents such as a prospectus a k or a q all sec documents are accessible online through our investor relations page of our website or through the secs edgar database when are the next samestore sales and earnings release dates destination xl group inc issues press releases on a quarterly basis to announce its sales and earnings for each respective quarter does destination xl group inc offer dividends or a stock reinvestment plan not at this time when does destination xl group inc fiscal year end our fiscal year ends on the saturday closest to january  do you have another question that hasnt been answered please submit your question using the form below  required fields name    email    subject    comments    type in number      this helps destination xl group inc prevent automated submissions   javascript is not enabled with javascript enabled this page will display content dynamically product information sizing chart personal shopper rewards center gift cards customer service contact customer service  update email preferences track order shipping information return policy glossary online stores destination xl rochester big  tall casual male xl shoesxl livingxl store locations destination xl casual male xl rochester big  tall sign up for email offers join us about us contact us investor relations store locations careers privacy policy security policy terms of use california transparency act site map all contents   cmrg apparel llc all rights reserved   about cookiescloselearn moreclosewhere is the credit card security codeclosewhat is a source codeclose destination xl group inc  company overview company overview press releases events analyst coverage faqs contact us dxl marketing campaign internati