lected to focus their business on those stores selling off their other businesses and assuming the casual male name in  the company acquired rochester big  tall clothing which gave the company access to a number of designer brands including robert graham tommy bahama cutter  buck jack victor and robert talbott also in  casual male hired former champion boxer george foreman to promote the chain and act as spokesman for new lines of clothing bearing his name in  casual male changed the name of its stores from casual male big  tall to casual male xl in  the company opened its first dxl store in schaumburg illinois big  tall customers were looking for a superior shopping experience – one that provided a better blend of quality selection and service this new store opening marked the starting point of the company’s transition from casual male xl to dxl in may  the company launched its first television and radio advertising campaign entitled “no man’s land” which supported the dxl brand as of  there were more than  dxl retail stores in operation across every major metropolitan market in the united states referencesedit  destination xl group inc stock quote  summary data nasdaq retrieved april    casual male retail group inc announces name change to destination xl group inc bloomberg business february    a b destination xl group inc  def a  for  sec info retrieved    find a store destination xl   cmrg profile  casual male retail grp inc profile  dxlg company information  destination xl group inc company information marketwatch retrieved    a b c d destination xl   globe  the boston globe may   retrieved    company profile for destination xl inc cmrg retrieved    larry dignan december   casual male ceo can it keep inventory fit baseline retrieved    mark jewell august   in with xl out with big  tall for mens largesize clothier san diego uniontribune associated press retrieved   external linksedit official site destination xl  company history at fundinguniversecom retrieved f