such as belts ties socks fashionneutral items including jeans casual slacks teeshirts polo shirts dress shirts and suit separates casual clothing and lifestyle products comprising chairs outdoor accessories travel accessories bed and bath products and fitness equipment the company offers its products under the destination xl dxl dxl outlets casual male xl casual male xl outlets rochester clothing shoesxl and livingxl trade names it also provides sportswear and loungewear sportcoats dress shirts neckwear tailoredrelated separates blazers dress slacks vintagescreen tshirts and wovens camp shirts printed woven shirts and relaxed islandinspired pants under various private labels destination xl group inc operates through  dxl retail stores  dxl outlet stores  casual male xl retail stores  casual male xl outlet stores and  rochester clothing stores as well as its destinationxlcom and bigandtallcom ecommerce sites the company was formerly known as casual male retail group inc and changed its name to destination xl group inc in february  destination xl group inc was founded in  and is headquartered in canton massachusetts detailed description  turnpike streetcanton ma united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwdestinationxlcom key executives for destination xl group inc mr david a levin president ceo  director age  total annual compensation k mr peter h stratton jr cfo senior vp  treasurer age  total annual compensation k mr kenneth m ederle chief merchandising officerplanning  allocation and senior vp age  total annual compensation k mr robert s molloy senior vp general counsel  secretary age  total annual compensation k mr brian s reaves chief sales officer  senior vp age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  destination xl group inc key developments destination xl group inc announces board retirements jun   on june   each of jesse choper and george porter jr notified destination xl group inc that they would not stand for reelection to the company